      • stackTrace

        public List<String> stackTrace()
        Description copied from interface: ITagHandler
        Answer a List of Strings, one for each level of tag nesting. The first string represents the tag document itself and the last string represents the receiver. Each level, except the first, indicates the line number and starting column of the tag as well as the body of the tag flattened to a single line
        Specified by:
        stackTrace in interface ITagHandler
        Returns:
        List describing the nested tags from the document tag to the receiver.
